data.meta_description:
16 likes, 1 comments - quickbooksca on December 10, 2020: "Colleen from @colleenschocolates is a chocolatier based in #Edmonton. Truly an artist, her chocolates boast novel flavours designed to be an experience, not just chocolate. Sourcing ingredients as much as possible from local vendors, Colleen values the vibrancy that Edmonton has to offer and works to incorporate the tones of her community into her chocolate design. Connection is important to Colleen and these values come through in her chocolates.

Make sure to #shopsmall this holiday season by tapping on the link in bio to check out Colleen’s Chocolates’ featured item in our QuickBooks Small Business Gift Guide. While you’re there, be sure to explore additional gift giving ideas for everyone on your list. #SMBHopeForTheHolidays #BackSmallBiz".
